author: David Fischer
title: Fabolous and Trey Songz Ring in 2017 with ‘Trappy New Years’ Mixtape
text:
After their 2009 collaboration on Trey Songz’ “Say Ahh,” Fabolous and Trey Songz are back together and celebrating the start of 2017 with their Trappy New Years mixtape.
when you Stay in the Bay a extra Day to cook up wit Trey.. sh ttt, sum'n might be on the Way @treysongz #Oakland 
A photo posted by Fabolous (@myfabolouslife) on Dec 23, 2016 at 8:46pm PST 

You can now listen and download the 6 song EP, featuring remixes of Migos’s “Bad and Boujee,” Young Jeezy’s “All There,” and more, here below.
